# Secrets — credentials, keys, and sensitive files that must never be committed
# or indexed. Includes paths targeted by known malware (litellm #24512).

## Cloud credentials
.aws/
.aws-credentials
.aws/config
.aws/credentials
.azure/
.config/gcloud/application_default_credentials.json
.digitalocean/
.digitalocean/access.yaml
.gcloud/credentials
.kube/config
.vercel/

